quran[7{c,v,t}:
1,1,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
1,2,tareef Allah hi ke liye hai jo tamam kaayenaat ka Rab hai
1,3,Rehman aur Raheem hai
1,4,roz jaza ka maalik hai
1,5,hum teri hi ibadat karte hain aur tujhi se madad mangte hain
1,6,hamein seedha rasta dikha
1,7,"unn logon ka rasta jin par to ne inaam farmaya, jo matob nahi hu-ay, jo bhatkay hu-ay nahi hain"
